{"tid":1303791,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【電影】向政府說不 線上看","createTime":"2019-07-10T12:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T12:18:42.000Z","uid":267337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2398453231c39f3c9ddb878685d453b75f0ceb23","tid":1303791,"uid":267337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E87bjEg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE87bjEg.png&h=50a49039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經歷多年軍事強人皮諾切特的獨裁統治，1988年智利舉辦公投，人民要用「Yes」或「No」決定未來八年是否繼續受強人統治。面對壓逼的政權，還有麻木冷漠的人群，反對黨領袖請來年輕廣告人，動用一系列廣告和宣傳來傳達反抗信念，喊「No」要自由。這一回，他們的戰場就在人民眼皮底下，讓視覺尬政權，奔放彩虹圖案對上冷硬政治口號，用想像力解放鐵幕之下停止跳動的心。"},{"pid":"206a74e46ea83389f444b78e8dabde3e21ecdeb9","tid":1303791,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>NOW</strong> - <ins>麥小姐追思會</ins> ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場 - 19:00~22:30</span></span><br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>梁烈士公眾告別禮</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=2b155652\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>油尖旺區議會夢遊</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D